### ============================================
### PASO 1: CREAR ITEMS (Si no existen)
### ============================================

### Crear Item 1: Arroz
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arroz Blanco",
  "description": "Arroz blanco de grano largo",
  "unitOfMeasurement": "kg",
  "expirationDays": 365,
  "category": "11",
  "idealStock": 100
}

