### ============================================
### VERIFICAR DATOS - CONSULTAS DE LECTURA
### ============================================

### Obtener todos los items con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener lotes próximos a expirar (ALERTA)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/close-to-expire
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener todos los lotes expirados
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/expired
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener todos los lotes del Arroz (ItemStock ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener todos los lotes del Pollo (ItemStock ID 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener lote próximo a expirar del Arroz
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/1/next-to-expire
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================
### EJEMPLOS DE CONSUMO - FIFO
### ============================================

### Consumir 30kg de Arroz (FIFO automático)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/1/decrease?quantity=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Consumir 50kg de Pollo (FIFO automático)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/2/decrease?quantity=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Consumir 25L de Leche (FIFO automático)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/item-stock/3/decrease?quantity=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================
### EJEMPLOS DE ESTADO Y DESCARTE
### ============================================

### Marcar lote de Arroz como próximo a expirar
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/1/status?status=PROXIMO_A_EXPIRAR
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Descartar lote de Pollo (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

